---
layout: base.njk
title: 今週のGitHubトレンド
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
---

<div class="hero">
    <h2 class="hero-title">今週のGitHubトレンドリポジトリ</h2>
    <p class="hero-description">GitHubで最も注目を集めている上位数件のリポジトリを、技術的な価値や実用性の観点から詳しく解説します</p>
    <p class="hero-date">{{ latestDate | dateFormat }}</p>
</div>

<section class="trends-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="repo-list">
            {%- for repo in latestTrends -%}
                {% set date = latestDate %}
                {% include "components/repo-card.njk" %}
            {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="recent-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">過去のトレンド</h2>
        <ul class="date-list">
            {%- for date in recentDates -%}
                <li>
                    <a href="{{ ('/trends/' + (date | dateFormat) + '/') | url }}" class="date-link">
                        {{ date | dateFormat }} ({{ trends.dateRepoCount[date] }}件)
                    </a>
                </li>
            {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
        <div class="section-footer">
            <a href="{{ '/archive/' | url }}" class="btn btn-outline">すべてのアーカイブを見る →</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>